  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Taipei Midsummer Night's Dream】is a brand-new real-life interactive love game. You will experience a unique love journey from a first-person perspective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is set in the bustling and quiet Taipei City. You will play a young tourist from mainland China (male protagonist: Wang Wei), and meet five female characters with different personalities in this modern and historical city. Each heroine has a unique background story and personality traits. They may be kind and gentle girls next door, or mysterious professional women. Each of your choices will directly affect the development of the plot and the final outcome. The design of multiple endings makes every game experience full of freshness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Character introduction</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mysterious Miss-Xia Ri</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141580/extras/21e0a080a181594437c3f13dfcd90b9d.poster.avif?t=1764299998\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141580/extras/21e0a080a181594437c3f13dfcd90b9d.webm?t=1764299998\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141580/extras/21e0a080a181594437c3f13dfcd90b9d.mp4?t=1764299998\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Betel Nut Beauty-Zhi Xin</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141580/extras/2fa4e5d408fc563eee848eac432563d8.poster.avif?t=1764299998\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141580/extras/2fa4e5d408fc563eee848eac432563d8.webm?t=1764299998\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141580/extras/2fa4e5d408fc563eee848eac432563d8.mp4?t=1764299998\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bartender-Zhong Yuan</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141580/extras/86904faf6e9cb7ec28a71fcc6bc39ac0.poster.avif?t=1764299998\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141580/extras/86904faf6e9cb7ec28a71fcc6bc39ac0.webm?t=1764299998\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141580/extras/86904faf6e9cb7ec28a71fcc6bc39ac0.mp4?t=1764299998\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Single Mother-Meng Ying</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141580/extras/a8b23c2c63acd3bf891febbbf81ec19b.poster.avif?t=1764299998\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141580/extras/a8b23c2c63acd3bf891febbbf81ec19b.webm?t=1764299998\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141580/extras/a8b23c2c63acd3bf891febbbf81ec19b.mp4?t=1764299998\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fitness Coach-Ye Zi</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141580/extras/20ba5b0aeebadb4d3941f7b965ad2ea8.poster.avif?t=1764299998\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141580/extras/20ba5b0aeebadb4d3941f7b965ad2ea8.webm?t=1764299998\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141580/extras/20ba5b0aeebadb4d3941f7b965ad2ea8.mp4?t=1764299998\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Five people with different charms, who will you fall in love with in the end?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or... maybe you will fall in love with someone other than the five people..?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
